Disclaimer and Request

Always credit ArbuzBudesh when posting images generated with this LoRA.

Trained on 100% publicly available images taken from e621.

Please do not sell this LoRA, or images generated with this LoRA (additionally, do not sell access to this LoRA, or access to images generated with this LoRA, e.g. via Patreon or other paid/subscription services).

Please do not remove metadata from images generated with this LoRA.

Model Info

  • Trained on: CoffeeNSFW (My fav. anime model)

  • Epoch: 10

  • Repeats: 5

  • Resolution: 640

  • Images: 470 from e621

    • I specifically filtered out images with the following tags:

      • video

      • animated

      • filetype:gif

      • date: older than 01/01/2016

      • lowres

  • Steps: 23500

  • ClipSkip: 2

Recommendations

  • Trigger Words: None needed

  • Weight: Around 0.9 yielded good results

  • Samplers:

    • Euler A showed surprisingly strong

    • Otherwise DPM++ 2M Karras was my go-to

  • Base Resolutions: Around 384x576

  • Upscalers:

    • 4x_fatal_Anime_500000_G showed the best results

    • 4x_fooldhardy_Remacri also did OK, but more washed out

    • Latent (nearest-exact) is also an OK option, but only at very high denoise

  • Extensions:

    • Use Dynamic Thresholding Extension to use high CFGs without burn-in

items.name: CrossoverMix
items.description:
Hi there, and welcome to my first ever checkpoint!

What I decided to do with this is create an illusionary combination of Western cartoon and anime styles, and also add 3D photorealism to the mix. It's something that I personally like to call:

CrossoverMix.

Recipe (and I credit everyone who made these models):

0.55(0.6(toonyouB31.MGIm) + 0.4(AnythingV5)) + 0.45(realisticVisionV20_v20) + 0.7(revAnimated_v122 - lyriel_v15)

(v2.0 update) - Added epicRealism - pure Evolution and AbsoluteReality into the mix to make the model to enhance the realism, lighting, and shadows to my subjects.

Recommended samplers: Euler A, or DPM++ 2M Karras

Clip skip: 2

CFG Scale: 5-7

Upscale by: 2

Denoising strength: (if you're doing hires. fix, do ~0.55-0.7)

I didn't bake any VAE in, but I highly recommend these VAEs:

vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

Night Sky VAE (located at the download link)

Suggestions and feedback are welcome! Hope you enjoy!

items.name: Elixir — Enhancer LoRA 🧪
items.description:
Introducing Elixir 🧪 — a LoRA that helps revitalize antiquated models, infusing them with renewed vitality. While for newer models, it offers a gentle yet discernible enhancement.

👋 Hey there! I'm Chillpixel, a developer, just diving into the vibrant CivitAI community.

Elixir was created using NinjaFix, my super cool algorithm that extracts the absolute best neurons from a bunch of neural networks, then mixes them together to create a totally fresh model.

I use Elixir by default, which plays nicely with other LoRAs and resources.

I hope you enjoy my first LoRA release — and if you do, please give Elixir a 5-star review!

HOW TO USE ELIXIR:

  • <lora:Elixir:1>

  • Turn up or down depending on how old the model is.

WHAT'S IN IT?

With Elixir V1, we start with a collection of exceptional LoRAs. Stuff that looks like an obvious enhancement.

We then use NinjaFix to dismantle these resources, extract the most prized neurons, and merge them to form a super LoRA, which I now entrust to you.

WHAT'S NEXT?

Elixir V1's effect is subtle and only scratches the surface of what's possible. We have many more resources to explore and create on the path to V2.

I hope to keep Elixir up to date with all the latest advancements: encompassing noise, lighting, styles, textures, intricate details, and other refinements.

Let's Have Fun!

I'm kicking off daily art themes and challenges now:

👉 https://discord.gg/89Pu5ehUvE

items.name: MixTape /// Rock n' Roll
items.description:
A world of 2D illustrations that come to life with an explosion of colors and a magical three-dimensional touch.

Let's create a gallery full of inspiration! Post your masterpieces and let's fill civitai with imagination, creativity, expression and joy!

Creativity is the stage where imagination and innovation meet, just as rock 'n' roll is the stage where artists channel their passion and energy. Both are powerful means of expression, capable of transmitting intense emotions and touching people deeply. Just as rock music can make us vibrate and stir our emotions, creativity involves us in a whirlwind of ideas, awakening sensations and taking us to new dimensions.

The Classic Rock version creates illustrations that offer a burst of vibrant color with a smoother, more subtle three-dimensionality.

The Hard Rock version creates illustrations that have an accentuated three-dimensional appearance. The shapes and textures present in the images are accentuated and have a bolder and more striking appearance.

The Punk Rock version creates illustrations with more detail, slightly softer colors, and a more subtle three-dimensional effect.

Recommends

Positive Prompt:

(masterpiece, best quality:1.4), (beautiful, perfect, delicate, detailed, intricate, aesthetic:1.2), ...

Negative Prompt:

EasyNegative, BadHands, BadArtist, BadArtistAnime, BadPrompt, BadImages, (low quality, worst quality:1.4), (monochrome, grayscale, sketch:1.2), (logo, signature, text, words, username, artist name, watermark), (loli:1.2), ...

Embeddings (Textual Inversion): EasyNegative, BadHands, BadArtist, BadArtistAnime, BadPrompt, BadImages

Sampling method: DPM++ SDE Karras

Sampling steps: 30 ~ 50

Hires. fix:

Sampler: 4x-UltraSharp

Hires steps: 10

Denoising strength: 0.5

Upscale by: 2 (resize from 512x768 to 1024x1536)

Clip skip: 2

CFG Scale: 7 ~ 8

VAE: kl-f8-anime2 VAE

Merge Recipe

Merged models are the following:

  • Beta+

  • Counterfeit-V3.0

  • DucHaitenNiji

  • fantasticmix2.5D

  • NabiMix

Classic Rock Steps:

  1. BaseModel = Counterfeit x 0.7 + NabiMix x 0.3

  2. MixTape = DucHaitenNiji x 0.3 + BaseModel x 0.7

Hard Rock Steps:

  1. BaseModel = Counterfeit x 0.7 + NabiMix x 0.3

  2. MixTape = DucHaitenNiji x 0.7 + BaseModel x 0.3

Punk Rock Steps:

  1. BaseModelA = Counterfeit x 0.7 + NabiMix x 0.3

  2. BaseModelB = DucHaitenNiji x 0.7 + BaseModelA x 0.3

  3. BaseModelC = Beta+ x 0.5 + fantasticmix2.5D x 0.5

  4. MixTape = BaseModelB x 0.7 + BaseModelC x 0.3

License

All used models here have "Have different permissions when sharing merges" license permission, so I do not try to add any restriction on it.

CreativeML-Open Rail-M

This model permits users to:

✔Use the model without crediting the creator

✔Sell images they generate

✔Run on services that generate images for money

✔Share merges using this model

✔Sell this model or merges using this model

✔Have different permissions when sharing merges

items.description:
🥷 Ninja V1 by Chillpixel

Get hyped for an unforgettable ride through the trendiest Checkpoints and LoRAs of the moment, all jam-packed into a legendary model that's about to blow your mind.

items.name: Robin (Fire Emblem: Awakening) LoRA
items.description:
Female Robin from Fire Emblem: Awakening, trained on animefull.

Around 0.8 weight works well. Trigger word is 'robin fe'. Adding 'robe', 'hood down', 'belt', and 'tactician' helps with generating her default outfit. Counterintuitively, trying to add 'tank top' and 'robe' at the same time makes the robe look weird pretty consistently, which is what the 'tactician' tag is good at fixing.

I've been in love with both of the Robin's designs since Awakening came out, so I'm glad this LoRA turned out alright. That said, it doesn't give too much detail to the coat, and for the life of me I could not figure out how to get it to give her her pants lol. Also, depending on the lighting and model, her hair can end up a tad discolored which is weird because I only used images with white hair during training ('white hair' in the prompt should fix this). It actually probably does a better job with generating her beach outfit, probably because it's much less busy lol. Still, while her base outfit can look weird at times, she herself looks amazing and overall I like this LoRA a lot.

items.name: CityEdge_DollyMix
items.description:
日本語の説明は後半にあります。

This is a merge model for generating bright-toned doll-like / 3D-animation-film-like illustrations.

Although this model is doll-like, it is not as if the doll were placed as is, but rather as if only the texture of the 2.5D illustration, including the background, were transformed to be doll-like. A block-merge with multiple doll-like models is utilized with an awareness of balance as well as stable response to prompts.

The main models merged are as follows.

  • foxyaNSFW v3, DucHaitenNiji v2.35, AOAOKO PVC Style, FaceBombMix v1, etc.

Both SFW and NSFW outputs are capable as NSFW models are included in the merge. High quality and unique images can be output in a short prompt. VAE is not needed, but you can try some.

List of my models

  • CityEdgeMix : Simple photo-realistic model based on Chilled family

  • CityEdge_ToonMix : Simple 2.5D anime-like model based on CityEdgeMix

  • CityEdge_2dToonMix : Pure 2D anime-like model merging only 2D models

  • CityEdge_StyleMix : Anime-like model with detail depiction by making use of block-merge

  • CityEdge_FusionMix : 2.5D model focusing on unique depiction through merging many models and block-merge.

  • Landscape_Photoreal : Model that produces photorealistic output, whether with characters or just the background

  • CityEdge_DollyMix : Model that produces doll-like and 3D animated movie-like output

明るいトーンのドール調・3Dアニメ映画調のイラストを生成するためのマージモデルです。

ドール調ではあるものの、人形がそのまま置いてあるようなイメージではなく、背景まで含めて描写された2.5Dイラストの質感だけをドール調にしたようなバランスを意識し、複数のドール調のモデルを階層マージしています。プロンプトへの安定した反応も意識しました。

マージしている主なモデルは以下のとおり。

foxyaNSFW v3, DucHaitenNiji v2.35, AOAOKO PVC Style, FaceBombMix v1

NSFWモデルをマージに含めているため、エロ・非エロどちらでも可。VAEは焼き込み済ですが別のものも試してみていいと思います。

モデル一覧

  • CityEdgeMix : Chilled系をベースにしたシンプルなフォトリアル系マージモデル

  • CityEdge_ToonMix : CityEdgeMixを2.5D化したシンプルな2.5Dアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_2dToonMix : 2Dモデルだけをマージしたピュア2Dアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_StyleMix : 階層マージを駆使してディテール描写にこだわったアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_FusionMix : 多数のモデルのマージと階層マージによる独自の描写にこだわった2.5Dモデル

  • Landscape_Photoreal : キャラクターがいても、背景だけでも、フォトリアルな出力が得られるモデル

  • CityEdge_DollyMix : ドール調・3Dアニメ映画調の出力が得られるモデル

items.description:
This model is made to achieve the skin detail seen from my initial model Ikigai 2.5D paired with the Danni 2D lora that's no longer available, without any lora needed!

Toned back the mix a bit, added in Real Moon. Also integrated a lora I used in Ikigai 2.5D for detail that no longer exists on the site.

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras
Sample Steps: 20-35
Upscaler: ESRGAN_4x

items.description:
用了刘*菲，刘*诗，全*贤，宋*乔做的女性lora，希望大家喜欢

tip1:注意步数再20到28 即可，过低的步数出图会扭曲，过高的步数会出现过拟合，

tip2:然后是lora的权重最好再0.6~0.9之间，太低出图就不像中国人了，太高就很像原图没有随机性，

可以参考我做的图的参数

最后，记得点赞，点赞，点赞呀，

This is a message about a female Lora created using Liu*Fei, Liu*Shi, Quan*Xian, and Song*Qiao. The author hopes that everyone will like it.

Tip 1: Pay attention to the number of steps between 20 and 28. If the number of steps is too low, the image will be distorted, and if it is too high, overfitting may occur.

Tip 2: The weight of Lora should ideally be between 0.6 and 0.9. If it's too low, the image won't look like a Chinese person, and if it's too high, it will look too much like the original image without randomness. You can refer to the parameters of the image I made.

Finally, remember to like, like, like!

items.description:
This model is a result of multiple mixes and lora merges to get cute faces with big round eyes, high contrast, thick black lines with a high level of detail.

The pros :
- Lora stacking without too much mess
- Good with both SFW and NSFW
- Very little prompting required
- Highly detailed skin & clothing textures

The cons :
- Might give some unwanted animal ears

Recommended parameters :

VAE : kl-f8-anime2.pt

(Optional: Masterpiece, best quality)

(worst quality, low quality:1.4, Easynegative, monochrome)

Sampler : Dpm++ 2M Karras Steps : 30

Sampler : Dpm++ SDE Karras Steps : 25

Sampler : UniPC Steps : 30

CFG scale : 6.5-7.5

Clip Skip : 2

Hires.fix: Ultra_Remacri (See Training data) or SwinIR_4X Denoising strength : 0.45

I'd highly recommend to also use Adetailer at default parameters with the "face_yolov8s" model.


Tips :
- For better quality eyes and iris, simply specify eye colors
- Keep the negative simple, stacking negative TI will have the opposite effect
